# Security Policy

## üîí Supported Versions

Please refer to the official lifecycle page to identify supported and actively maintained releases:
- [https://bitcoincore.org/en/lifecycle/#schedule](https://bitcoincore.org/en/lifecycle/#schedule)

Security updates are provided only for the listed maintained versions. Users are **strongly advised to upgrade** to supported versions to receive patches.

---

## üö® Reporting a Vulnerability

If you discover a security vulnerability, please **report it responsibly** via encrypted email:

- Email: `security@bitcoincore.org`
- **This address is for vulnerability disclosure only.** For general support, use [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues) or forums.

Please include:
- A clear description of the issue
- A proof-of-concept or reproduction steps
- Affected version(s)
- Potential impact (if known)

---

